# Coalesce contributors who committed under more than one name/address, so that
# git shortlog, git log --use-mailmap and GitHub's Contributors view group them
# under a single identity. (The old irstea.fr -> inrae.fr change was applied to
# the history itself, so it needs no entry here.)
#
# Format:  Proper Name <canonical@email> [<other@email>]

